snippet.title: SOLITUNE - a game about escapism - Trailer
snippet.description:
SOLITUNE is a short game about leaving behind what doesn't make you happy to become a shepherd. Well, sort of, in a weird way.

!!! Can you help us getting SOLITUNE greenlit on Steam? Please vote YES for us :D !!! 
- http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=860831515

The song in the video is 'Copy&Paste'.

Get the game on itch.io: https://ratking.itch.io/solitude
With a soundtrack by Ludwig Hanisch - https://ludwig-hanisch.de
